Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,GOODBYE LASSIE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Was its owner using this boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because I found its leash in this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When I read the name written on it,\Nit replied immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is it you, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know who owns that boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:02:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was here just a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it has no owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.01,0:02:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew when I looked at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The boat's rope was cut off, indicating\Nthat the owner was running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps not to run away,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the rope it teared by itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact I don't know\Nthe answer to your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did this boat come from?\NI wish I could find the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, where did you came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it wise to move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But we must find the owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, if we know where it came from
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we may find the mother of Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, if you find the owner\Nyou will give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have no other choice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,True, if Lassie lives with its mother,\Nit will live happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an airplane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The delivery goods that were\Nin my house are on the plane now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My father is a contractor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered, I met you for the first time\Nwhen I saw the plane flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If the plane wasn't there,\NI would't meet Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the school road!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That bridge we always see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! John and Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get this boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to Lassie's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found the owner of the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure we'll find Lassie's mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me! I'll go with you!\NWait! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There is the backyard of the houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,First time I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him, I saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so beautiful, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The village looks quite different by the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Hooper!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, you're Carraclough's son, isn't it?\NThat's a good boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This remainds me... what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered, I saw a puppy on board\Nof this boat two or three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hooper, have you seen it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it came on this river.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,John!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's important not to tell\Nyour mother that you saw me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? You are a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We crossed a long distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How long we'll continue this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a steamer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is dangerous, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cross this road, you will be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it with this wheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here! This rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same rope as on the boat,\Nit's cut in the same shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that means...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the two ropes are exactly the samel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So Lassie was coming from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to find your mother soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We finally found her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's so annoying, so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You two! Children, you are making\Nnoise around other people's houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's my boat that I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we came to look for\Nthe owner of this boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for this... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, do you know anything about Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I know, because it's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.59,0:08:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to say this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I understand, I will return it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.73,0:08:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It stayed with me for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,after it almost crumbled\Nunder the feet of the sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So please let me say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I will give it some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When you finish it, bring it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great, Lassie, we've found your owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Give your mother a lot of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.72,0:09:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, now go to your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey go! Don't you want to meet your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, not that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the child!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't play here, move right away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a place to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, I'll do it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The water level must rise quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, our steam pump is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, I have no time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come here and help me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen Lassie, this is just a wheel,\Nso you have to go to your owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So pull more and work hard, kid!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter? Can't you move it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the gate to raise the water level!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This side must be closed\Nwhen this ship comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We must send the high water\Nto the opposite side!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter? Have you closed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But, why do you do that, Colin?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I did this because the uncle\Nasked me to do so, to use my force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, have you called this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And as it looks, they can leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want to rest more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pff...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.91,0:12:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you satisfied with this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't you think of coming here again,\Ngo away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, will you use it for guarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask about things that don't concern you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you live here alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a family other than this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong with that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is no other choice for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well get here immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you'll do bad things, I'll eat you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must open the rest of the gates quickly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that man knows\Nhow to behave with the poor Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it, I should tell him so!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,John?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? You are the child\Nwho came earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie drinks milk from a child's bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But you try to train it to eat from the dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You, uncle, will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How long will you keep bothering me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no time to train it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't drink milk\Nby its own, is it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it over? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, how will I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, this world is not that easy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,John...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let 's go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, John, let's go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.41,0:14:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But that sounds fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, why do you look\Nat other people's houses?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That an amazing machine like this\Ncould be found in someone's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you let me look at it a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to leave immediately, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, is there a house for the dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A dog house? There is no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey? No house for the dog?\NWhere did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you want from me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for your likes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do if a ship\Npassed by and didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Another question? Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to me, uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to ask you something else!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.17,0:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,John, enough, let 's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it's really important!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I will answer only one question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, what do you have\Nto eat for today, uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.82,0:16:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you wanted to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's canned food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Canned food?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, today canned food\Nand every day canned food!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time to cook\Nso my food is just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is great...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:17:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like it's good, there's no food to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, why are you interested by my food?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have food to eat,\Nyou may have to eat Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think I'll really eat the puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is the truth but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't see Lassie's mother here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see Lassie's mother here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Lassie's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't eat it, because I don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle! I don't see it! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find Lassie's mother\Nand bring it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The puppy's mother is really not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I looked around the place thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a liar! He's not the owner of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of that driver!\NThe driver...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Driver! Yes, that wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know that, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but it was strange of Lassie\Nto smell that wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A few days ago there was\Na car on this road with a flat tire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is said he was coming from a foreign\Ncountry and was accompanied by a Collie dog.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When the driver fix his car,\Nthis puppy fled away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The port was far away and\Nhe couldn't stay any longer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so he decided to leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He also asked me to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, this puppy belongs to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He left it under my care,\Nso I have no other choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop with that bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't take care of it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to promise me\Nthat you will take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid, in such a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would grow better with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I left Lassie with you, it would die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you wanted to take care of it\Ninstead of someone like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No? Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And now stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to take care of it\Nuntil it grows up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a honest kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He made me go and come with no reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,John, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, don't come here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take care of the puppy!\NGo, liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that before you promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! John!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you now, grab it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't do that before you promise me\Nto take good care of Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This time is not appropriate for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't bother you again if you promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Insubordination will only make matters worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to contradict me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look, it's a ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue your stubbornness,\Nyou will regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand, I promise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This uncle lives alone, so stay with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!\NAs if it would understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's yours!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I brought it to you\Nbecause you are its owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I have made you a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you are so proud of it\Nthen you can take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's annoying, it likes you\Nso I'll leave it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to the hut again, all three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You will taste some sea-food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we'll certainly come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Lassie, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be getting hot milk, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow is my mother's birthday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But my father lost his salary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He can't bring any gift.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie, you'll find it with your smell!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\NMY FATHER'S SALARY{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
